data.description: BeauThis beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property has been meticulously maintained and upgraded with many modern amenities. The open-plan living area is perfect for entertaining, and the kitchen is a chef’s dream, with high-end appliances and plenty of counter space. The bedrooms are spacious and comfortable, and the bathrooms are beautifully appointed with high-quality fixtures and finishes. The property also features a private outdoor space, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the beautiful Philadelphia weather.  This property is located in a great neighborhood, with easy access to local amenities and public transportation. It is also conveniently located near major highways, making it easy to get around the city.
